      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a variable M Differential Lock. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a complete VANOS rebuild and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity. The suspension features refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, maintaining the chassis's legendary handling precision. Recent service includes a valve adjustment and a cooling system overhaul with a high-flow water pump. A mechanically sound, driver-focused icon ready for the apex.",
