      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-maintained daily driver that strikes a perfect balance between luxury and reliability. The exterior finish presents beautifully with a deep gloss, showing only minor, expected signs of use such as light stone chips on the front fascia and a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the rear bumper. The body lines are perfectly straight, and the factory alloy wheels remain in excellent shape. Stepping inside, you are greeted by a pristine, smoke-free interior. The leather seating surfaces have been regularly conditioned to prevent wear, and the carpets have been protected by all-weather mats since day one. All power features, including the sunroof, heated seats, and navigation system, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in robust health; it has followed a strict synthetic oil change regimen every 5,000 miles. The engine is quiet and responsive, the transmission shifts are seamless, and the tires have approximately 70% tread life remaining. We have a folder of service receipts available for review. This is a solid, dependable vehicle that is ready for immediate delivery.",
